{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/etcd-io/etcd/issues/10932","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/etcd-io/etcd","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/etcd-io/etcd/issues/10932/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/etcd-io/etcd/issues/10932/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/etcd-io/etcd/issues/10932/events","html_url":"https://github.com/etcd-io/etcd/issues/10932","id":472873648,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU0NzI4NzM2NDg=","number":10932,"title":"embed: zap logger TLS handshake failure causes index out-of-bounds panic","user":{"login":"ChrisRx","id":1930145,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE5MzAxNDU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1930145?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ChrisRx","html_url":"https://github.com/ChrisRx","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ChrisRx/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ChrisRx/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ChrisRx/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ChrisRx/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ChrisRx/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ChrisRx/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ChrisRx/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ChrisRx/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ChrisRx/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2019-07-25T13:42:33Z","updated_at":"2019-07-25T13:56:32Z","closed_at":"2019-07-25T13:56:32Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"https://github.com/etcd-io/etcd/blob/8f000c755b78fbae4921bc6e0c5a182571774ce4/embed/config_logging.go#L245\r\n\r\nConstructing this slice the capacity is set rather than the length, so when reaching the loop directly below it will always fail due to slice index being out-of-bounds.\r\n\r\nConditions to reproduce:\r\n * Use embed package to run multiple etcd nodes\r\n * Set `embed.Config.Logger` to `zap`\r\n * Run using invalid certificates to trigger TLS handshake errors\r\n\r\nSpecifically, the SAN ip addresses were wrong for the TLS error that I ran into this with, so the first time a node tries to log an error related to TLS handshake it panics.\r\n\r\nThe fix is fairly simple since it is just a small mistake with how the slice is being created here, it just needs to have the length set instead of the capacity.","closed_by":{"login":"gyuho","id":6799218,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY3OTkyMTg=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6799218?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/gyuho","html_url":"https://github.com/gyuho","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gyuho/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gyuho/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gyuho/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gyuho/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gyuho/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gyuho/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gyuho/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gyuho/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gyuho/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/etcd-io/etcd/issues/10932/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/etcd-io/etcd/issues/10932/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_r